global-health/covid-19/about-remdesivir." ([2020]):[2] US Food and Drug Administration "Fact sheet for health care providers emergency use authorization (EUA) of remdesivir (GS-5734TM) Available from: URL: https://www.fda.gov/media/137566/download." ([2020, May 1]]):[3] European Medicines Agency "Summary on compassionate use. Remdesivir Gilead. Available from: URL: https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/documents/other/summary-compassionate-use-remdesivir-gilead_en.pdf." ([2020 Apr 03]):[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767369485);
