id, Dexrazoxane, Oxygen, Lanthanum carbonate, Difelikefalin, Cobicistat, Deferoxamine, Levoleucovorin, More', 'Thiothixene, Quetiapine, Prochlorperazine, Lumateperone, Cariprazine, Lurasidone, Mesoridazine, Methotrimeprazine, Pimavanserin, Clozapine, Triflupromazine, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/21975/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
